Ok, for those who ran into the same prob...I also did the hjjoin thing.  For the one who did...reload the torrent again and it will fix the 48th file to be the right size again or something.  Anyway, use WINRAR and select files 1-48 and choose an empty directory to extract to then let it go...it will get to a point where it says overwrite or replace the .BIN file and you say NO.  It will then proceed for a bit and crap out asking for .00 file, right?  Well, just keep hitting the NO button and it will keep on extracting anyway and eventually be done. Then you have a CUE and BIN file.  As I understand it, load up the CUE file using a CD BURNER and it will use the BIN file to burn the CD.  I am about to do try it but saw you guys were in the same fix I was and wanted to try and help.  Hope it works and good luck to us all!

Okay, it worked like a charm...for the CD crack and all just check the directory names Razor1911 on the newly burned CD.  Use the key generator and write the code down somewhere if you are going to use Battle.net.  Then follow the rest of the instructions in the .nfo file in the Razor1911 directory!  Have fun!

ok great. so im a newb right but i got it working!!!!
so to all newbs:
download torrent
download winrar
in winrar, select 1- 48 and extract to an empty folder
download daemon tools
open up the new daemon drive (found in My Computer)
in a different window open up the folder where the cue and bin file are
click and drag cue file to daemon drive
open the install program
for the serial password/w/e, go to My Computer and right click on Daemon drive and click explore
go to the razor1911 folder and go to the crack exe
use the thing
grab a penis and celebrate.
